#: services/static-webserver/client/source/class/osparc/product/quickStart/tis/PostPro.js:50
msgid ""
"        Alternatively, slice views of the maximum interferential E-field can"
" also be visualized and synchronous with the MAP slices         to assess "
"safety-related aspects (e.g., field intensity in proximity of the "
"electrodes). These maps can be edited, thresholded,         and saved "
"offline for further inspection and analysis.<br>        An isosurface of the"
" TI stimulation distribution for the selected configuration can also be "
"visualized within the head anatomy for inspection.      "
msgstr ""
"或者，最大干扰电场的切片视图也可以与MAP切片同步可视化，以评估与安全相关的方面（例如，电极附近的场强）。这些地图可以编辑、设定阈值，并离线保存以供进一步检查和分析。<br>选定配置的TI刺激分布的等值面也可以在头部解剖结构中可视化以供检查。"
"      "

